0.body: BugBee logo BugBee is a free Discord bot designed to help game developers manage feedback. Invite BugBee to your server BugBee does not store any report , it only forward them to a dedicated channel in your discord server. Please review the Privacy Policy for more details. Gather user reports from your game or from discord
0.title: What is BugBee?

10.body: shared_code: A shared_code required in the API calls returns: The game_id, required in the API calls Create an endpoint integration for the specifig Frontend Channel where the command was issued. It enable users to submit reports via the API. More details in API Reference .

20.body: Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boudary=<boundary word> Content-Length: <size of the body>
20.title: Header

21.body: game_id - string - Required Game ID returned by the /add_endpoint_integration command. endpoint_secret - string - Required The shared_code used when register a channel with the /add_endpoint_integration command. description - string - Required The content of the report written by the user. report_type - string - Required The type of report that is being created, can be Feedback or Bug. attachment - bytes - Optional Needed if attachment_filename is set. The binary array containing the raw data of the file to upload, up to 10MB. attachment_filename - bytes - Optional Needed if attachment is set. The name of the file uploaded in the attachment field.
21.title: Body

A simple Godot Example: func send_feedback_multipart(game_id: String, endpoint_secret: String, text: String, report_type: String, image: Image) -> void: var http_request = HTTPRequest.new() add_child(http_request) var body = PackedByteArray() body.append_array("--boundary".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachment"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("Content-Type: image/png
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array(image.save_png_to_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("--boundary".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="game_id"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array(game_id.to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("--boundary".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="endpoint_secret"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array(endpoint_secret.to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("--boundary".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array(text.to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("--boundary".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="report_type"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("

Content-Disposition: form-data; name="attachment_filename"
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("screenshot-{0}.png".format([Time.get_datetime_string_from_system()]).to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("
".to_utf8_buffer()) body.append_array("--boundary--".to_utf8_buffer()) var headers = [ "Content-Length: " + str(body.size()), "Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary" ] http_request.request_raw("https://api.bugbee.app/v1/report", headers, HTTPClient.METHOD_POST, body)

3.body: To register a channel where users can report feedback and bugs, create a dedicated Frontend Channel , and register it by typing: /add_game <your game name>
3.breadcrumbs: Getting Started » Add a Frontend Channel for a game
3.title: Add a Frontend Channel for a game

4.body: To enable in-game reporting, you need to add an endpoint integration. Go to the dedicated Frontend Channel for your game, then type /add_endpoint_integration <shared_code>, where the shared_code is a string of your choosing. The bot will reply with your game's id. Note down your shared_code and your game_id for later. You can now send report from you game to Bugbee's api. Please refer to the API Reference for more details.
4.breadcrumbs: Getting Started » Add an Endpoint integration
4.title: Add an Endpoint integration
